'''黄明威'''（{{lang-en|Brian A. Wong}}，{{bd|1974年|5月15日||catIdx=Wong, Brian}}）是美國產業互聯網的高級主管，企業家和天使投資人，現任阿里巴巴集團全球計劃副總裁兼阿里巴巴學術委員會成員。<ref>David Thomas,{{cite news|title=Alibaba tests water with e-commerce initiatives |url=https://africanbusinessmagazine.com/sectors/technology/alibaba-tests-water-with-e-commerce-initiatives/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=africanbusinessmagazine.com|date=12  November 2020}}</ref> 他也是RADII Media的創始人和董事長。<ref>{{cite news|title=Can China Balance Consumerism With Sustainability?|url=https://www.alizila.com/can-china-balance-consumerism-with-sustainability/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=alizila.com|date=12 November 2019}}</ref>

== 早期生活和教育 ==
黄明威在加州的帕羅奧圖出生並長大。他就讀於帕羅奧圖高中，畢業後也獲得了斯沃斯莫爾學院的醫學預科和英語文學學士學位。<ref>Jeffrey Lott,{{cite news|title=Alumni Worldwide|url=https://bulletin.swarthmore.edu/bulletin-issue-archive/index.html%3Fp=687.html|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=bulletin.swarthmore.edu|date=}}</ref> 他還獲得了南京大學—約翰斯．霍普金斯大學中美文化研究中心的國際關係碩士學位和賓州大學華頓商學院的工商管理碩士學位。<ref>{{cite news|title=Brian Wong WG'03 Vice President Alibaba|url=https://www.whartonnationbrandconference.com/brian-wong|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=whartonnationbrandconference.com|date=}}</ref> 

== 職業 ==
黄明威剛從大學畢業後，擔任舊金山市長威利•布朗（Willie L. Brown Jr.）的特別助理。<ref name="WE">{{cite news|title=Brian A. Wong Vice-President, Global Initiatives, Alibaba Group|url=https://www.weforum.org/people/brian-a-wong|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=weforum.org|date=}}</ref>  在這之後，他於1999年與馬雲（Jack Ma）和蔡崇信（Joe Tsai）在舊金山見面後加入了全球知名的中國電子商務公司阿里巴巴集團。<ref>Jesus Alcocer,{{cite news|title=The Man Behind Alibaba’s Leadership Initiative|url=https://magazine.wharton.upenn.edu/digital/30770/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=magazine.wharton.upenn.edu|date=10 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Alibaba Partners With World Economic Forum To Launch Davos Friends of Africa Growth Platform for African Entrepreneurs |url=https://afrikanheroes.com/2020/01/25/alibaba-partners-with-world-economic-forum-to-launch-davos-friends-of-africa-growth-platform-for-african-entrepreneurs/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=afrikanheroes.com|date=25 January 2020}}</ref> 他以第1位美國人和第52位員工的身份加入了該公司。<ref>{{cite news|title=Digitally China: The Inside View of China’s Development from 8 to 800 Million Internet Users|url=https://radiichina.com/digitally-china-inside-story-alibaba|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=radiichina.com|date=}}</ref>

黄明威目前是阿里巴巴集團的副總裁。<ref>Tom Brennan{{cite news|title=China Offers Clues To Africa’S Prospects For Digital Growth|url=https://www.alizila.com/china-offers-clues-to-africas-prospects-for-digital-economy-growth/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=alizila.com|date=6 September 2019}}</ref><ref>Matthew Michaels,Harrison Jacobs,{{cite news|title=The two biggest things Silicon Valley misunderstands about China, according to a top Alibaba exec|url=https://www.businessinsider.in/the-two-biggest-things-silicon-valley-misunderstands-about-china-according-to-a-top-alibaba-exec/articleshow/64292057.cms|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=businessinsider.in|date=23 May 2018}}</ref><ref>Josh Horwitz,{{cite news|title=On the Alibaba campus, ambition and humility are both on display|url=https://qz.com/1159008/all-about-alibaba-ambition-and-humility-in-the-companys-campus-and-culture/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=qz.com|date=9 December 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Jack Ma relies on Chinese philosophies for Alibaba's success
|url=https://www.afr.com/chanticleer/jack-ma-relies-on-chinese-philosophies-for-alibabas-success-20170531-gwhflm|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=afr.com|date=31 May 2017}}</ref> 他曾擔任阿里巴巴全球領導力學院（AGLA）執行董事，負責行政人員的領導發展。<ref>Rachel Feintzeig,{{cite news|title=For New Hires at Alibaba, a Crash Course in Chinese Business|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/for-new-hires-at-alibaba-a-crash-course-in-chinese-business-1484044203|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=wsj.com|date=10 January 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=From Hangzhou to Rwanda: what Jack Ma is bringing to Africa’s digital transformation|url=https://www.weforum.org/agenda/2019/09/jack-ma-africa-digital-transformation|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=weforum.org|date=3 September 2019}}</ref> 他曾擔任執行主席國際事務特別助理。<ref>Russell Flannery,{{cite news|title=Alibaba Expands Its Influence In Asia With An Offline Touch|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/russellflannery/2018/04/18/alibaba-expands-its-influence-in-asia-with-an-offline-touch/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=forbes.com|date=18 April 2018}}</ref> 同時也帶領著阿里巴巴邁向國際發展。<ref>{{cite news|title=How Jack Ma sees a thriving future of entrepreneurship in Africa|url=https://europeansting.com/2020/03/02/how-jack-ma-sees-a-thriving-future-of-entrepreneurship-in-africa|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=europeansting.com|date=2 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Davos 2020: Brian Wong On Turning Challenges Into Opportunities|url=https://www.alizila.com/video/davos-2020-brian-wong-on-turning-challenges-into-opportunities|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=alizila.com|date=}}</ref>

一直是各國政府的數碼轉型策略顧問，並在國際會議上擔任演講嘉賓。<ref>{{cite news|title=B20 Türkiye Konferansı|url=https://www.haber7.com/istanbul/1540639-b20-turkiye-konferansi|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=haber7.com|date=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Brian A. Wong
|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm9730712/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=imdb.com|date=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Enabling E-commerce: Opening the Door for SMEs|url=https://unctad.org/en/conferences/e-week2018/Pages/MeetingDetails.aspx?meetingid=1740|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=unctad.org|date=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Brian Wong: Advisor|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2016/12/07/brian-wong-mentor.html|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=cnbc.com|date=}}</ref>

黄明威是數碼媒體平台RADII的創始人和董事長。<ref>{{cite news|title=The website Radii wants us to focus on a China of innovation, lifestyle and transformative technology |url=https://www.thealternative.org.uk/dailyalternative/2019/6/23/radii-softpower-china|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=thealternative.org.uk|date=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Changing Perceptions; Bridging Nations|url=https://www.aspeninstitute.org/longform/summit-the-journey-from-thought-to-action-2018-edition/changing-perceptions-bridging-nations/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=aspeninstitute.org|date=24 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=2015年“全球青年领袖”名单公布|url=http://world.people.com.cn/n/2015/0317/c1002-26707892.html|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=people.com.cn|date=}}</ref> 他還是非營利組織Operation Masks的聯合創辦人，Operation Masks是由一群企業家期望為抵抗COVID-19作出貢獻而創建的。<ref>Mara Hvistendahl,{{cite news|title=The tech industry turns to mask diplomacy|url=https://www.technologyreview.com/2020/04/27/1000457/ppe-masks-huawei-alibaba-tencent-china-diplomacy|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=technologyreview.com|date=27 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Turn Crisis Into Opportunity: New Digital Handbook For Entrepreneurs During Covid-19|url=https://www.alizila.com/video/turn-crisis-into-opportunity-new-digital-handbook-for-entrepreneurs-during-covid-19/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=alizila.com|date=}}</ref> 

黄明威曾是華頓商學院校友會執行委員會成員<ref>{{cite news|title=Brian Wong: Advisor|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2016/12/07/brian-wong-mentor.html|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=cnbc.com|date=7 December 2016}}</ref>，目前是斯沃斯莫爾學院總統倡議委員會的成員。<ref>{{cite news|title=Brian A. Wong|url=https://www.globalteacherprize.org/person?id=2324|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=globalteacherprize.org|date=}}</ref> 他經常參與演講並擔任講師，演講議題涵蓋「數碼經濟在促進各項發展中扮演著甚麼角色」。<ref>{{cite news|title=Sunway iLabs partners players in digital ecosystem|url=https://www.theborneopost.com/2020/04/23/sunway-ilabs-partners-players-in-digital-ecosystem/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=theborneopost.com|date=23 April 2020}}</ref>

== 榮譽 ==
黄明威在2015年被世界經濟論壇評選為全球青年領袖。<ref name="WE"/> 他還被選為阿斯彭研究所第四屆中國研究員級成員，也是阿斯彭全球領導力網絡的成員。<ref>{{cite news|title=Brian A. Wong Vice President, Alibaba Group|url=https://agln.aspeninstitute.org/profile/1936|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=agln.aspeninstitute.org|date=}}</ref>  黄明威還是傑出的華裔美國人小組委員會100的成員。<ref>{{cite news|title=Brian Wong Vice President, Global Initiatives Alibaba Group|url=https://www.committee100.org/member/brianwong/|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=committee100.org|date=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=和马云、蔡崇信喝了杯茶后，他成为阿里第一个美籍员工 |url=https://www.sohu.com/a/190451916_114930|accessdate=21 May 2020|publisher=sohu.com|date=}}</ref>

